21 "39-2-18.
22 (a) Notwithstanding any other provisions of this chapter to the contrary, nothing in this
23 chapter shall apply to any minor employed as an actor or performer in motion pictures or
24 theatrical productions, in radio or television productions, in any other performance, concert,
